wiki.content: B.o.B told Artist Direct: "I'm still young, but in the song I'm reflecting on my younger days when I was all about chasing girls. I was a hopeless romantic and made a lot of stupid decisions. It's about those days. I'm compiling my observations of myself and putting them on a record." (Source Nothin' On You Songfacts).
